0) Prerequisites (must have)

*Java 17
*Maven
*Spring Boot 3.2.x (you already moved to 3.2.2 ✅)

1) Install Ollama (local AI runtime)

*Windows:- 
Download Ollama from the official website:
	https://ollama.com/download

*Restart system once (recommended).

*Mac:-
Install from the same link OR with Homebrew:
	brew install ollama

3) Download the model (llama3.1:8b)

*Run:
	 ollama pull llama3.1:8b
 
*Check installed models:
	ollama list

*Quick test:
	ollama run llama3.2

Type: hello → it should reply.

